  9 May 2002; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org> devfsd-1.3.25.ebuild :

  Update to latest version.

*devfsd-1.3.24 (19 Feb 2002)

  14 Jul 2002; phoen][x <phoenix@gentoo.org> devfsd-1.3.24.ebuild :
